    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was conducted to investigate the effects of daily supplementation of Zingiber
      officinale Roscoe extract on body fat.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study was a 12 weeks, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled human trial. Forty
      subjects were randomly divided into Zingiber officinale Roscoe extract 200 mg or 400 mg or
      placebo group. The investigators measured Body Fat Mass, Percent Body Fat, Fat Free Mass,
      weight, and body mass index.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
